        <a href="https://livejohnshopkins.sharepoint.com/sites/inside-privacy-office/SitePages/about-hipaa/Index.aspx?%3d%3d&sdata=em5XL3hWSlhtbFhZdVpxc3h0OE1WQU9ERGs5WFYwUnFiVWdsUk90SEdxaz0%3d" 
           target="_blank">JHM Covered Entity</a>? 
